VRChat is widely recognized as a welcoming space for individuals of diverse queer identities, with a significant portion of its user base identifying as queer. Numerous queer communities exist on the platform, including one of the most notable, "[[Special:MyLanguage/Community:Trans Academy|Trans Academy]]", a [[wikipedia:501(c)(3) organization|501(c)(3)]] non-profit organization, which has been recognized and supported by VRChat<ref>[https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/438100/view/4194619900926161010 'Celebrate Pride Month with Trans Academy from June 7-9!'] on Steam; retrieved September 12, 2024</ref>.